# ShipMaster — Navigation Structure

---

## Dispatcher View

### Dashboard
- Active shipments count
- In-transit map overview
- Recent activity

---

### Shipments
- **My Shipments** — all shipments, tabbed: Contracted / Open / All
- **New Shipment** — create contracted shipment, picks contract, auto-fills carrier and rate, calculates estimated cost via Google Distance Matrix

---

### Contracts
- **Agreements** — list of all contracts, status: Active / Expiring / Draft / Expired
- **New Agreement** — create contract, assign carrier, assign receiver (auto-invited on sign), set rate structure, sign digitally

---

### Carriers
- **My Carriers** — contracted carriers, verification status, active contracts per carrier, lifetime shipments

---

### Tracking
- **Live Map** — all in-transit shipments on one map, carrier dots moving in real time
- **Route Planner** — enter pickup and delivery, get distance and estimated cost before creating a shipment

---

### Finances
- **Payments** — invoices, escrow balances, released payments
- **Cost Reports** — per shipment cost breakdown, mileage × rate, totals by carrier and period

---

### Account
- **Settings** — company profile, notification preferences
- **Users** — manage dispatcher accounts within the organization

---

## Carrier Mobile App Sidebar *(separate app)*

- **My Jobs** — assigned shipments, status
- **Active Job** — current shipment, route, Start Tracking / Mark Delivered
- **Earnings** — per shipment payouts, total
- **Profile** — DOT, insurance, vehicle

---

## Receiver Web Sidebar *(minimal)*

- **My Deliveries** — pending and active shipments
- **Live Tracking** — map view for active shipment, ETA
- **History** — past deliveries

